| **Technical Depth** | 8/10 | MongoDB transactions, JWT dual-token, TOTP 2FA, atomic points, discriminator inheritance |
| **Real-World Value** | 8/10 | Solves a genuine healthcare problem with practical features |
| **Presentation Potential** | 7/10 | Strong Swagger docs, Postman collection, but no frontend demo in this repo |
| **Documentation** | 7/10 | Good README, API status doc, release notes, but no architecture diagrams |
| **Testing** | 3/10 | Only smoke/E2E scripts, no unit tests, no coverage |

### **Final Grade Estimate: 74/100 (B+)**

The project demonstrates **senior-level architectural thinking** in its layered design, security patterns, and gamification engine. The main deductions are for the absence of a test suite, the placeholder geo-matching, and the security credential leak.

